1
00:00:04,830 --> 00:00:05,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was that?</font>

2
00:00:05,880 --> 00:00:07,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, Erik. What's wrong?</font>

3
00:00:07,600 --> 00:00:09,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please open the door!</font>

4
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:11,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the matter?</font>

5
00:00:11,820 --> 00:00:17,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}THE CASE OF THE MUSICIAN
AND THE LOCKED-ROOM MURDER</font>

6
00:00:11,890 --> 00:00:15,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard a crash and my boyfriend
 won't open the door.</font>

7
00:00:15,250 --> 00:00:16,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait right here.</font>

8
00:00:20,780 --> 00:00:22,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Bernhardt, I'm coming in.</font>

9
00:00:41,220 --> 00:00:43,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}THE CASEBOOK OF ARNE</font>

10
00:02:01,300 --> 00:02:06,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}PART 10: DIFFERENT COUNTRIES,
 DIFFERENT CUSTOMS</font>

11
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:06,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So the doppelgänger of a culprit
 will also become a culprit?</font>

12
00:02:06,980 --> 00:02:11,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're identical inside and out, 
so it's the obvious conclusion.</font>

13
00:02:11,850 --> 00:02:13,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I guess so.</font>

14
00:02:14,340 --> 00:02:16,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! But you know what 
that means, Lord Arne?</font>

15
00:02:16,790 --> 00:02:21,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was right when I deduced
they were <i>both</i> guilty.</font>

16
00:02:21,440 --> 00:02:22,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

17
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:25,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My reward. I'd like my reward now.</font>

18
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:27,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?</font>

19
00:02:27,370 --> 00:02:29,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You promised me one!</font>

20
00:02:29,840 --> 00:02:33,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said if I worked out if the original 
or the doppelgänger was the killer,</font>

21
00:02:33,050 --> 00:02:34,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you'd give me a reward!</font>

22
00:02:34,910 --> 00:02:36,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said nothing of the sort.</font>

23
00:02:36,550 --> 00:02:38,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You <i>so</i> did!</font>

24
00:02:40,760 --> 00:02:43,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What's going on over there?</font>

25
00:02:43,210 --> 00:02:44,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who knows?</font>

26
00:02:44,510 --> 00:02:46,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A tenant was murdered?</font>

27
00:02:46,780 --> 00:02:50,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, and it sounds like 
it's a locked-room mystery.</font>

28
00:02:50,420 --> 00:02:53,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A locked-room mystery? How horrible.</font>

29
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:56,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Lord Arne?</font>

30
00:02:56,710 --> 00:03:00,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay now, move along. 
Nothing to see here.</font>

31
00:03:00,530 --> 00:03:03,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You, too. You're in the way, pal.
 Move along.</font>

32
00:03:03,410 --> 00:03:06,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Was this really a locked-room murder?</font>

33
00:03:06,200 --> 00:03:07,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

34
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:10,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, yes. But you're not authorized to—</font>

35
00:03:10,920 --> 00:03:15,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, wait. Aren't you that 
renowned master detective, sir?</font>

36
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:18,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. I came to help
 with the investigation.</font>

37
00:03:18,160 --> 00:03:21,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? D-Did he spread that rumor
 in that instant?</font>

38
00:03:21,490 --> 00:03:23,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder what's gotten into him.</font>

39
00:03:23,950 --> 00:03:25,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Thank you for coming.</font>

40
00:03:25,630 --> 00:03:27,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This way. Allow me to show you in.</font>

41
00:03:27,610 --> 00:03:31,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, out of our way! Make a path!</font>

42
00:03:31,010 --> 00:03:33,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just to kill some time. 
You can go on home.</font>

43
00:03:33,940 --> 00:03:38,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of <i>course</i> Lord Arne would be all like,
 "Might as well finish this crossword,"</font>

44
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:41,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">as he strolls off to solve
 a locked-room mystery!</font>

45
00:03:41,990 --> 00:03:43,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's the very <i>model</i> of a detective!</font>

46
00:03:43,730 --> 00:03:46,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They sure are unique creatures,
 these detectives.</font>

47
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:48,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a pain.</font>

48
00:03:48,450 --> 00:03:50,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go with him.</font>

49
00:03:50,030 --> 00:03:52,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please wait for us, Lord Arne!</font>

50
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:59,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The victim was a tenant here:
 Erik Bernhardt.</font>

51
00:03:59,130 --> 00:04:03,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He died from a stab wound to the back of 
the neck made by a thin, knifelike object.</font>

52
00:04:03,530 --> 00:04:06,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">According to the police, 
when his body was discovered,</font>

53
00:04:06,950 --> 00:04:09,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the door and all of 
the windows were locked.</font>

54
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:14,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The witnesses used a spare key to get in,
 from what I'm told.</font>

55
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:16,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're really starting 
to sound the part, Lynn.</font>

56
00:04:16,770 --> 00:04:19,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Thank you for saying so.</font>

57
00:04:19,010 --> 00:04:22,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And these are the two witnesses 
who discovered the body.</font>

58
00:04:22,140 --> 00:04:26,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I'd promised to meet him here today.</font>

59
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:31,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I arrived, I kept calling his name
 but he just wouldn't answer.</font>

60
00:04:31,070 --> 00:04:36,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard her voice and a strange noise,
so I came to see what had happened.</font>

61
00:04:36,010 --> 00:04:38,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I used my spare key to get in.</font>

62
00:04:38,910 --> 00:04:40,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A strange noise?</font>

63
00:04:40,370 --> 00:04:43,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I heard a loud crash, 
like something had shattered.</font>

64
00:04:44,110 --> 00:04:45,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Probably these plates.</font>

65
00:04:46,090 --> 00:04:48,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It looks like he kept them
 on this cabinet.</font>

66
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:51,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe they fell off 
as he struggled with his killer.</font>

67
00:04:51,550 --> 00:04:53,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, seems unlikely.</font>

68
00:04:53,310 --> 00:04:53,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

69
00:04:54,400 --> 00:04:58,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If they'd bumped it, the items inside 
the cabinet would also have been disturbed.</font>

70
00:04:58,760 --> 00:05:02,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And these fragments landed on top of his leg.</font>

71
00:05:02,830 --> 00:05:06,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'd be more logical to assume
the plates fell for another reason</font>

72
00:05:06,630 --> 00:05:08,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>after</i> the man had been murdered.</font>

73
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:10,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-That makes sense.</font>

74
00:05:11,640 --> 00:05:15,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His body also bears few injuries 
and his clothes look fine.</font>

75
00:05:15,740 --> 00:05:17,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's unlikely he struggled with his killer.</font>

76
00:05:19,970 --> 00:05:20,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this?</font>

77
00:05:21,750 --> 00:05:23,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like some kind of pet food.</font>

78
00:05:23,670 --> 00:05:26,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pet food? Did he have a pet?</font>

79
00:05:26,940 --> 00:05:29,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that <i>is</i> strange.</font>

80
00:05:29,150 --> 00:05:31,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pets aren't allowed in the building.</font>

81
00:05:31,760 --> 00:05:33,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, he didn't have a pet.</font>

82
00:05:34,130 --> 00:05:36,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He didn't like animals, period.</font>

83
00:05:37,250 --> 00:05:39,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He didn't, huh?</font>

84
00:05:41,690 --> 00:05:44,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Erik was a musician, wasn't he?</font>

85
00:05:44,910 --> 00:05:47,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, he was a trumpet player.</font>

86
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:50,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His playing was always so wonderful.</font>

87
00:05:57,100 --> 00:05:58,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Arne, I was just thinking...</font>

88
00:06:02,340 --> 00:06:03,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a strange painting.</font>

89
00:06:04,530 --> 00:06:10,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not sure why, but the style
 reminds me of something.</font>

90
00:06:11,270 --> 00:06:13,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What were you about to say?</font>

91
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:15,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that's right.</font>

92
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:18,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, I overheard the police
 saying something.</font>

93
00:06:19,050 --> 00:06:24,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The victim, Mr. Erik, had fallen behind
 on his rent not long ago.</font>

94
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:27,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And since the room was locked,</font>

95
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:31,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">wouldn't that cast suspicion on the landlady,
since she had a spare key?</font>

96
00:06:31,590 --> 00:06:33,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said the room was locked, right?</font>

97
00:06:33,980 --> 00:06:35,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Uh, yes.</font>

98
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:38,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The door and all the windows 
were apparently locked.</font>

99
00:06:39,140 --> 00:06:43,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it seems the room
 wasn't entirely sealed.</font>

100
00:06:43,310 --> 00:06:44,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

101
00:06:46,110 --> 00:06:47,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An air vent?</font>

102
00:06:48,020 --> 00:06:49,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, we'll have to investigate.</font>

103
00:06:49,970 --> 00:06:51,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go on, Lynn Reinweiß.</font>

104
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go and enjoy your "paradise."</font>

105
00:06:53,810 --> 00:06:57,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! I don't actually <i>like</i> dust, you know!</font>

106
00:06:57,520 --> 00:07:00,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On top of that, 
that's way too small for me to fit!</font>

107
00:07:00,500 --> 00:07:03,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is? Then, Amy, remove your head.</font>

108
00:07:03,630 --> 00:07:05,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't be absurd.</font>

109
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:09,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But luckily, I have a stuffed animal
 that should fit perfectly.</font>

110
00:07:13,110 --> 00:07:14,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? What was that?!</font>

111
00:07:14,860 --> 00:07:17,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks so much for helping, Nach.</font>

112
00:07:17,790 --> 00:07:21,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Wait, you moron. Stop! Don't!</font>

113
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:21,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There.</font>

114
00:07:23,930 --> 00:07:26,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How dare you jerks do this to me!</font>

115
00:07:26,670 --> 00:07:29,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Find out where it goes. Get on with it.</font>

116
00:07:30,140 --> 00:07:33,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tch. Gimme a stinkin' break.</font>

117
00:07:37,700 --> 00:07:40,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It looks like it leads out back.</font>

118
00:07:41,170 --> 00:07:42,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go take a look.</font>

119
00:07:46,170 --> 00:07:48,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You actually made yourself 
useful for a change.</font>

120
00:07:48,580 --> 00:07:51,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up. Never make me do that again.</font>

121
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:57,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. So this is the back of the building.</font>

122
00:07:59,220 --> 00:08:00,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Arne?</font>

123
00:08:02,800 --> 00:08:04,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What's that?</font>

124
00:08:04,900 --> 00:08:08,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's an ice pick. You use it 
to break ice into pieces.</font>

125
00:08:08,580 --> 00:08:10,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It smells just like the corpse.</font>

126
00:08:10,890 --> 00:08:13,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! That must mean 
it's the murder weapon!</font>

127
00:08:14,840 --> 00:08:16,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got it.</font>

128
00:08:16,890 --> 00:08:21,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The killer tied a string to the ice pick,
 shot it through the air vent,</font>

129
00:08:21,760 --> 00:08:27,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">murdered the victim, 
then reeled the ice pick back in,</font>

130
00:08:28,230 --> 00:08:30,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">before discarding it here.</font>

131
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:32,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The mystery of the 
locked-room murder is solved!</font>

132
00:08:32,920 --> 00:08:34,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

133
00:08:34,290 --> 00:08:37,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The killer aimed at the man's neck 
through the vent from outside the building.</font>

134
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:38,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

135
00:08:38,900 --> 00:08:41,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a brilliant pile of nonsense,
 Dimwit Reinweiß.</font>

136
00:08:41,810 --> 00:08:43,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not even a centaur could pull that off.</font>

137
00:08:43,370 --> 00:08:45,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guess you're right.</font>

138
00:08:45,150 --> 00:08:48,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I still think the suspicious ones 
are the landlady with her spare key,</font>

139
00:08:48,640 --> 00:08:52,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the girlfriend who said she was 
with the victim last night... Hmm?</font>

140
00:08:52,530 --> 00:08:55,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Wow! When did 
all these kitties show up?</font>

141
00:08:56,150 --> 00:08:57,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are more over there.</font>

142
00:08:57,960 --> 00:09:01,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if this is where 
the local cats always gather.</font>

143
00:09:01,560 --> 00:09:03,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, so cute.</font>

144
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:07,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here, kitty. Aw! Yes, dat's wight!</font>

145
00:09:08,070 --> 00:09:10,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't do it. No!</font>

146
00:09:10,430 --> 00:09:13,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop biting me! Stop kicking me!</font>

147
00:09:13,030 --> 00:09:15,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Bleh, fur! I got fur in my mouth!</font>

148
00:09:13,420 --> 00:09:15,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm? What's this?</font>

149
00:09:15,740 --> 00:09:18,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's filthy with dust. Just like Nach.</font>

150
00:09:18,910 --> 00:09:21,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Ouch! Don't scratch me!</font>

151
00:09:19,300 --> 00:09:24,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That means the ice pick must have
been dragged through the air vent.</font>

152
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:24,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I said ouch! Stop! Someone save me!</font>

153
00:09:24,660 --> 00:09:26,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hey, don't ignore me!</font>

154
00:09:24,660 --> 00:09:26,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It appears so.</font>

155
00:09:27,170 --> 00:09:30,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look, Lord Arne. Isn't it cute?</font>

156
00:09:36,430 --> 00:09:37,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

157
00:09:38,610 --> 00:09:40,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They all left.</font>

158
00:09:40,410 --> 00:09:43,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, could you please <i>not</i> 
scare them away like that?</font>

159
00:09:43,100 --> 00:09:44,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't do a thing.</font>

160
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:48,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Naturally cautious animals 
are instinctively afraid of me.</font>

161
00:09:48,690 --> 00:09:50,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, they are?</font>

162
00:09:51,150 --> 00:09:53,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We might be able to find something else.</font>

163
00:09:53,650 --> 00:09:55,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's look around here a little longer.</font>

164
00:10:05,460 --> 00:10:06,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be careful.</font>

165
00:10:06,890 --> 00:10:09,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Try not to scratch it. Just go slowly.</font>

166
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:12,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Is that Heinz?</font>

167
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:15,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Lynn?</font>

168
00:10:15,940 --> 00:10:17,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It <i>is</i> you, Miss Lynn.</font>

169
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:20,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! It's been so long, Heinz!</font>

170
00:10:20,970 --> 00:10:24,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, it has. I'm glad to 
see you looking so well.</font>

171
00:10:24,560 --> 00:10:27,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! I said be careful, okay?</font>

172
00:10:27,020 --> 00:10:28,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure! Sorry 'bout that!</font>

173
00:10:28,590 --> 00:10:29,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, guys.</font>

174
00:10:30,290 --> 00:10:32,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never thought I'd run into you here.</font>

175
00:10:32,800 --> 00:10:34,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you moving?</font>

176
00:10:34,400 --> 00:10:40,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no. I actually just found 
a truly wonderful refrigerator.</font>

177
00:10:40,700 --> 00:10:46,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's glossy, pure white, 
and it makes the most wonderful ice.</font>

178
00:10:46,570 --> 00:10:49,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And it finally arrived today.</font>

179
00:10:51,680 --> 00:10:54,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you're still cooking, Heinz?</font>

180
00:10:54,500 --> 00:10:58,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course. After I parted ways 
with the Reinweiß estate staff,</font>

181
00:10:58,240 --> 00:11:01,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I traveled the world to study cooking.</font>

182
00:11:01,090 --> 00:11:04,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right now, I work as a chef
 at a nearby hotel.</font>

183
00:11:04,040 --> 00:11:05,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow!</font>

184
00:11:05,140 --> 00:11:08,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This city has so many delicious restaurants.</font>

185
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:13,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like the pizza place on the main street 
or the ice cream parlor near the park.</font>

186
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:15,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, but enough about me.</font>

187
00:11:15,230 --> 00:11:17,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you still with...</font>

188
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:20,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, it appears you did stick with him.</font>

189
00:11:20,640 --> 00:11:25,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! Right now, I'm working as one
 of Lord Arne's assistant detectives.</font>

190
00:11:25,280 --> 00:11:26,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are?</font>

191
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:31,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, if you're detectives, are you 
investigating that murder case?</font>

192
00:11:31,570 --> 00:11:32,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, we are.</font>

193
00:11:32,930 --> 00:11:37,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. That man unfortunately 
did seem to have some issues.</font>

194
00:11:37,170 --> 00:11:41,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Was he a friend of yours, Heinz?</font>

195
00:11:41,170 --> 00:11:44,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, no, I wouldn't say we were friends.</font>

196
00:11:44,860 --> 00:11:48,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're talking about 
the murdered trumpet player, right?</font>

197
00:11:48,010 --> 00:11:50,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's this bar down the street...</font>

198
00:11:50,530 --> 00:11:53,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're actually famous 
for their delicious potatoes.</font>

199
00:11:53,560 --> 00:11:58,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But um, anyway, I used 
to see him play there often.</font>

200
00:11:58,240 --> 00:12:00,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was very talented, but...</font>

201
00:12:00,730 --> 00:12:01,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm?</font>

202
00:12:01,420 --> 00:12:05,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One time, I saw him 
and the owner arguing.</font>

203
00:12:05,890 --> 00:12:08,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seemed to have something
 to do with money.</font>

204
00:12:09,290 --> 00:12:10,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ice pick.</font>

205
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:11,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

206
00:12:11,660 --> 00:12:14,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm? Did something happen
 with an ice pick?</font>

207
00:12:14,710 --> 00:12:16,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, never mind.</font>

208
00:12:16,430 --> 00:12:19,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much for 
the useful information, Heinz.</font>

209
00:12:19,530 --> 00:12:21,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go investigate right away!</font>

210
00:12:21,180 --> 00:12:24,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, sure. I'm glad I was able to help.</font>

211
00:12:24,590 --> 00:12:26,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll come and see you again.</font>

212
00:12:26,420 --> 00:12:28,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd love to eat your cooking again.</font>

213
00:12:28,350 --> 00:12:31,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure. It'd be my pleasure.</font>

214
00:12:31,150 --> 00:12:32,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me!</font>

215
00:12:33,160 --> 00:12:35,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to get your signature for this.</font>

216
00:12:36,110 --> 00:12:38,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, sure!</font>

217
00:12:38,010 --> 00:12:39,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See you later, okay?</font>

218
00:12:45,910 --> 00:12:47,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me!</font>

219
00:12:48,790 --> 00:12:50,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you work at this bar?</font>

220
00:12:50,630 --> 00:12:52,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I do.</font>

221
00:12:52,600 --> 00:12:56,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, is the owner in right now?</font>

222
00:12:56,100 --> 00:12:58,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would like to speak to him if possible.</font>

223
00:12:58,520 --> 00:13:02,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The owner? The owner is actually 
on vacation at the moment.</font>

224
00:13:02,500 --> 00:13:05,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. He's on vacation?</font>

225
00:13:05,410 --> 00:13:07,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. He left last week.</font>

226
00:13:07,490 --> 00:13:09,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He should be back in two days, though.</font>

227
00:13:09,760 --> 00:13:11,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

228
00:13:11,790 --> 00:13:14,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that's true, he can't be the killer.</font>

229
00:13:17,020 --> 00:13:23,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Actually, we're investigating 
the murder of Erik Bernhardt.</font>

230
00:13:24,600 --> 00:13:26,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, so that's what this is about.</font>

231
00:13:27,610 --> 00:13:30,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He could be a little high-strung,</font>

232
00:13:30,860 --> 00:13:32,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but he really was an excellent player.</font>

233
00:13:32,920 --> 00:13:36,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Many young women would come here
just to see him perform.</font>

234
00:13:36,030 --> 00:13:37,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It really is unfortunate.</font>

235
00:13:37,870 --> 00:13:39,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

236
00:13:39,140 --> 00:13:44,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did Mr. Erik ever get into 
any trouble with the owner here?</font>

237
00:13:44,890 --> 00:13:47,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Hmm, I wonder.</font>

238
00:13:47,840 --> 00:13:51,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A while back, he got upset 
about his pay being late,</font>

239
00:13:51,660 --> 00:13:53,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but they resolved that.</font>

240
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:56,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please tell me all about it!</font>

241
00:13:56,360 --> 00:14:00,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, well, I don't know 
all the details myself,</font>

242
00:14:00,570 --> 00:14:05,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it seems the owner made 
some mistake and didn't pay him fully.</font>

243
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:09,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But he paid him later on, and even gave him 
a little extra, so they made up.</font>

244
00:14:10,580 --> 00:14:12,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On the day of the trouble,</font>

245
00:14:12,640 --> 00:14:15,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the owner had been drinking
and Erik hadn't been sleeping well,</font>

246
00:14:15,560 --> 00:14:17,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so it turned into a full-blown argument.</font>

247
00:14:18,280 --> 00:14:20,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess that's no surprise.</font>

248
00:14:20,410 --> 00:14:23,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But those two had known
 each other for years,</font>

249
00:14:23,840 --> 00:14:27,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and there were no grudges between them 
that would lead to something like murder.</font>

250
00:14:27,680 --> 00:14:31,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That gives me a clearer picture.
Thank you very much.</font>

251
00:14:31,400 --> 00:14:32,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I ask something?</font>

252
00:14:32,610 --> 00:14:34,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. What is it?</font>

253
00:14:34,550 --> 00:14:36,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did this come from your bar?</font>

254
00:14:37,040 --> 00:14:39,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? No, that isn't ours.</font>

255
00:14:40,430 --> 00:14:43,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. Thanks for your time.</font>

256
00:14:44,500 --> 00:14:46,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much.</font>

257
00:14:46,180 --> 00:14:47,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, not at all.</font>

258
00:14:49,910 --> 00:14:53,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, that was a dead end, 
but at least we got a few more clues.</font>

259
00:14:53,940 --> 00:14:57,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The late rent must have been 
because he hadn't been paid.</font>

260
00:14:57,880 --> 00:15:01,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess the next question is if he'd had 
any disagreements with the landlady.</font>

261
00:15:02,100 --> 00:15:03,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose so.</font>

262
00:15:03,220 --> 00:15:06,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He did say one other 
interesting thing, though.</font>

263
00:15:06,030 --> 00:15:09,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About many female customers 
being interested in him.</font>

264
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:12,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. He may have had 
girlfriend problems.</font>

265
00:15:12,670 --> 00:15:14,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's another possibility.</font>

266
00:15:14,640 --> 00:15:18,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Either way, we need to keep 
gathering information!</font>

267
00:15:19,400 --> 00:15:21,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, perfect timing.</font>

268
00:15:21,750 --> 00:15:23,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me!</font>

269
00:15:24,390 --> 00:15:26,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's the detectives.</font>

270
00:15:26,570 --> 00:15:28,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well? Have you learned anything?</font>

271
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:32,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, we're still trying
 to gather information.</font>

272
00:15:32,020 --> 00:15:35,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, there's something 
I'd like to ask you.</font>

273
00:15:35,350 --> 00:15:36,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What might that be?</font>

274
00:15:37,060 --> 00:15:38,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, um...</font>

275
00:15:38,360 --> 00:15:44,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were told there was a time recently 
when Mr. Erik was unable to pay his rent.</font>

276
00:15:44,400 --> 00:15:49,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that? I already told 
the police all about that.</font>

277
00:15:49,520 --> 00:15:54,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He said he was waiting to get paid
 and asked me for some extra time.</font>

278
00:15:54,710 --> 00:15:58,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since he explained his reasons to me 
and paid everything he owed later on,</font>

279
00:15:58,790 --> 00:16:00,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it was never really a problem.</font>

280
00:16:00,740 --> 00:16:03,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. I-It wasn't?</font>

281
00:16:03,630 --> 00:16:05,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope that doesn't disappoint you.</font>

282
00:16:05,400 --> 00:16:07,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were you starting to suspect me, maybe?</font>

283
00:16:07,880 --> 00:16:10,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no! Definitely not!</font>

284
00:16:12,650 --> 00:16:14,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, more kitties.</font>

285
00:16:15,920 --> 00:16:17,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shoo! Shoo! Get out of here!</font>

286
00:16:19,840 --> 00:16:22,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those darned cats.</font>

287
00:16:22,170 --> 00:16:25,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know when they started
 coming around here,</font>

288
00:16:25,300 --> 00:16:27,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but they're always such a nuisance.</font>

289
00:16:27,450 --> 00:16:28,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A nuisance?</font>

290
00:16:28,580 --> 00:16:31,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yes. They dig through 
the trash and leave a mess,</font>

291
00:16:31,650 --> 00:16:35,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and worst of all, they growl 
and make noise every night.</font>

292
00:16:35,370 --> 00:16:36,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I see.</font>

293
00:16:41,760 --> 00:16:43,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it, Lynn?</font>

294
00:16:43,410 --> 00:16:45,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The pet food in the room.</font>

295
00:16:45,080 --> 00:16:48,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe Mr. Erik actually 
really loved pets,</font>

296
00:16:48,500 --> 00:16:50,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but since he wasn't allowed to keep one,</font>

297
00:16:50,580 --> 00:16:53,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he went out every night
 to feed the cats?</font>

298
00:16:53,680 --> 00:16:56,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? I certainly hope not.</font>

299
00:16:56,050 --> 00:16:57,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

300
00:16:57,120 --> 00:16:59,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I don't think that adds up.</font>

301
00:16:59,120 --> 00:17:01,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Why not?</font>

302
00:17:01,710 --> 00:17:03,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go look into it right now.</font>

303
00:17:04,110 --> 00:17:05,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back to the victim's room.</font>

304
00:17:05,790 --> 00:17:07,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Oh, okay!</font>

305
00:17:07,920 --> 00:17:11,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That stuffed animal 
of yours sure is cute.</font>

306
00:17:11,240 --> 00:17:12,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you serious?</font>

307
00:17:12,560 --> 00:17:13,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

308
00:17:15,880 --> 00:17:19,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Arne, did you figure something out?</font>

309
00:17:19,530 --> 00:17:20,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take a look.</font>

310
00:17:25,240 --> 00:17:29,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I made my blood stick to any dust
 from the air vent.</font>

311
00:17:29,740 --> 00:17:32,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't those footprints?</font>

312
00:17:32,310 --> 00:17:33,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That settles it.</font>

313
00:17:33,520 --> 00:17:35,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Arne, what does this mean?</font>

314
00:17:35,760 --> 00:17:38,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lynn Reinweiß, check inside
 that pet food bag.</font>

315
00:17:38,950 --> 00:17:40,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Oh, okay.</font>

316
00:17:44,370 --> 00:17:46,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's something in here.</font>

317
00:17:47,410 --> 00:17:49,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this?</font>

318
00:17:49,440 --> 00:17:50,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me see.</font>

319
00:17:56,080 --> 00:17:56,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's poison.</font>

320
00:17:56,690 --> 00:17:58,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-P-P-P-P-P-Poison?</font>

321
00:17:58,970 --> 00:18:00,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wash up when we're done.</font>

322
00:18:00,390 --> 00:18:02,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, yes, I will!</font>

323
00:18:02,120 --> 00:18:05,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But are you okay, Lord Arne?</font>

324
00:18:05,090 --> 00:18:07,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Poison doesn't work on vampires.</font>

325
00:18:07,020 --> 00:18:08,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, of course not!</font>

326
00:18:08,360 --> 00:18:11,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only things like silver 
and garlic work on vampires!</font>

327
00:18:12,370 --> 00:18:13,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now I understand.</font>

328
00:18:13,720 --> 00:18:16,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The man wasn't trying to feed the cats.</font>

329
00:18:16,350 --> 00:18:17,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was trying to kill them.</font>

330
00:18:18,230 --> 00:18:19,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

331
00:18:19,160 --> 00:18:22,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A high-strung musician who hates animals.</font>

332
00:18:22,600 --> 00:18:26,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not hard to imagine the noisy cats
 driving him crazy every night,</font>

333
00:18:26,520 --> 00:18:27,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so he tried to kill them.</font>

334
00:18:28,130 --> 00:18:31,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So the room wasn't 
completely sealed after all.</font>

335
00:18:31,020 --> 00:18:36,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The killer pranced right in and killed 
the man before it could be killed itself.</font>

336
00:18:37,680 --> 00:18:38,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that right?</font>

337
00:18:48,690 --> 00:18:52,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That cat has been following us
 the whole time.</font>

338
00:18:52,990 --> 00:18:57,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It never got close, so I thought
 it was just being cautious.</font>

339
00:18:57,140 --> 00:19:01,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, but I told you there's no way 
any normal cat would follow me around.</font>

340
00:19:03,450 --> 00:19:05,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-The cat is...</font>

341
00:19:05,330 --> 00:19:08,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a cat-sìth, a kind of cat fairy.</font>

342
00:19:08,420 --> 00:19:09,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A cat-sìth?</font>

343
00:19:10,240 --> 00:19:13,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like the detective says,</font>

344
00:19:13,060 --> 00:19:16,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I killed him before 
he could kill all of us, meow.</font>

345
00:19:16,690 --> 00:19:20,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I could've gotten the humans 
to suspect each other more,</font>

346
00:19:22,000 --> 00:19:26,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would've loved to have killed 
that female they call the landlady, too.</font>

347
00:19:27,250 --> 00:19:29,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Too bad, meow.</font>

348
00:19:34,440 --> 00:19:38,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hey! Cut it out! I won't let you forget this!</font>

349
00:19:38,820 --> 00:19:41,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Quit tickling me! That tickles!</font>

350
00:19:41,200 --> 00:19:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so cold! But so good!</font>

351
00:19:41,200 --> 00:19:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}How dare you treat me like this!</font>

352
00:19:43,680 --> 00:19:45,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should've gotten some 
gelato, too, Lord Arne.</font>

353
00:19:45,890 --> 00:19:46,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope.</font>

354
00:19:46,610 --> 00:19:49,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What if it were made from blood?</font>

355
00:19:49,530 --> 00:19:50,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who would eat that?</font>

356
00:19:53,890 --> 00:19:57,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if we shouldn't have 
let the cat-sìth get away.</font>

357
00:19:57,850 --> 00:20:02,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From a human point of view, 
it's nothing but a murderer.</font>

358
00:20:02,000 --> 00:20:04,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But from a feline point of view,</font>

359
00:20:04,490 --> 00:20:07,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that cat-sìth is a hero who saved 
many of its kind from slaughter.</font>

360
00:20:08,230 --> 00:20:09,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A feline point of view?</font>

361
00:20:09,980 --> 00:20:12,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you want cats menacing you
 night after night?</font>

362
00:20:12,180 --> 00:20:12,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

363
00:20:21,840 --> 00:20:25,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can all relax. 
We have no interest in your cat hero.</font>

364
00:20:28,960 --> 00:20:31,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. I'm not interested in cats.</font>

365
00:20:31,960 --> 00:20:34,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What I am interested in is...</font>

366
00:20:36,570 --> 00:20:38,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Arne?</font>

367
00:20:38,540 --> 00:20:40,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go home, Lynn Reinweiß.</font>

368
00:20:40,760 --> 00:20:43,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a feeling 
we're about to get very busy.</font>

369
00:20:47,740 --> 00:20:51,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup! A beer after work
 sure hits the spot.</font>

370
00:20:51,410 --> 00:20:53,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How long are you gonna
 keep drinking anyway?</font>

371
00:20:54,260 --> 00:20:57,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it's still "after five"
until the next day's shift begins.</font>

372
00:20:57,990 --> 00:20:59,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me! I'll have another!</font>

373
00:20:59,800 --> 00:21:00,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

374
00:21:00,650 --> 00:21:05,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I guess it worked out 
since I was hoping to eat this again.</font>

375
00:21:05,150 --> 00:21:09,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you remember what we were 
delivering here the last time?</font>

376
00:21:09,250 --> 00:21:11,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, what was it?</font>

377
00:21:11,710 --> 00:21:15,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right. Wasn't it some kind
 of weird painting?</font>

378
00:21:32,400 --> 00:21:36,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TRANSLATION: MICHAEL ARNOLD</font>

379
00:21:36,030 --> 00:21:40,120
